<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hartung <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglolfst<ex>ein</ex></expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Waldegk
